704
00:30:36,580 --> 00:30:37,260
Nothing.

705
00:30:37,580 --> 00:30:39,440
I just think this is interesting.

706
00:30:52,340 --> 00:30:53,300
What do you think

707
00:30:54,620 --> 00:30:56,540
of Xiao Tu?

708
00:30:59,180 --> 00:31:00,140
Xiao Tu.

709
00:31:00,660 --> 00:31:01,860
She's quite special.

710
00:31:06,700 --> 00:31:08,100
Does Ye Jun

711
00:31:08,340 --> 00:31:11,340
also have such a bad taste that he has a crush on Xiao Tu?

712
00:31:12,740 --> 00:31:13,340
Wait.

713
00:31:14,340 --> 00:31:15,470
Why did I say "also"?

714
00:31:19,050 --> 00:31:23,810
[Exclusive Epilogue]

715
00:31:36,580 --> 00:31:37,240
Godfather.

716
00:31:40,580 --> 00:31:42,220
When I watched this TV drama,

717
00:31:42,220 --> 00:31:43,580
I saw that the heroine often

718
00:31:43,580 --> 00:31:46,300
leaned her head on the shoulder of a boy.

719
00:31:46,460 --> 00:31:48,660
I wanted to give it a try to see if it feels comfortable.

720
00:31:48,660 --> 00:31:49,220
You're not okay.

721
00:31:49,220 --> 00:31:50,060
You're too thin.

722
00:31:50,060 --> 00:31:50,820
Your bones made me feel uncomfortable.
